#: ../../source/misc/apt.rst:72
msgid "IoC (Indicators of Compromise) 在取证领域被定义为计算机安全性被破坏的证据。"
msgstr ""
"IoC (Indicators of Compromise) is defined in forensics as evidence that "
"computer security has been compromised."

